%h1 Homkora API Documentation
%p
	:markdown
		Projects
		=======

		*****

		**Retrieve Projects:**

		Required Params: auth_token

			Example Code:

				curl http://homkora.com/projects.json?auth_token=APIKEYHERE

			Expected Result:

				[
					{
						"_id":"5143c295d7fd1f987f222221",
						"created_at":"2013-03-16T00:53:41Z",
						"description":"test",
						"title":"test",
						"total_time":"00:00:00",
						"updated_at":"2013-03-16T00:53:41Z",
						"user_id":"5143bf4dd7fd1f786722221"
					}
				]

		*****

		**Add Projects:**

		Required Params: auth_token - title - description

			Example Code:

				curl \
					-v -H "Accept: application/json" -H "Content-type: application/json" \
					-X POST -d '{"project":{"description":"value2","title":"value1"}}' \
					http://homkora.com/projects.json?auth_token=APIKEYHERE

			Expected Result:

				{
					"_id":"5143c6b5d7fd1f5c80000005",
					"created_at":"2013-03-16T01:11:17Z",
					"description":"value2",
					"title":"value1",
					"total_time":"00:00:00",
					"updated_at":"2013-03-16T01:11:17Z",
					"user_id":"5143bf4dd7fd1f786722221"
				}

		*****

		**Edit Projects:**

		Required Params: auth_token - title and/or description

			Example Code:

				curl \
					-v -H "Accept: application/json" -H "Content-type: application/json" \
					-X PUT -d '{"project":{"description":"edit"}}' \
					http://homkora.com/projects/PROJECTID.json?auth_token=APIKEYHERE

			Expected Result:

				{
					"_id":"5143c6b5d7fd1f5c80000005",
					"created_at":"2013-03-16T01:11:17Z",
					"description":"edit",
					"title":"value1",
					"total_time":"00:00:00",
					"updated_at":"2013-03-16T01:12:17Z",
					"user_id":"5143bf4dd7fd1f786722221"
				}

		*****

		**View Project:**

		Required Params: auth_token

			Example Code:

				curl http://homkora.com/projects/PROJECTID.json?auth_token=APIKEYHERE

			Expected Result:

				{
					"_id":"5143c6b5d7fd1f5c80000005",
					"created_at":"2013-03-16T01:11:17Z",
					"description":"edit",
					"title":"value1",
					"total_time":"00:00:00",
					"updated_at":"2013-03-16T01:12:17Z",
					"user_id":"5143bf4dd7fd1f786722221"
				}

